    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Cyttaromyia fuscula Cockerell, 1921 (new combination), USNM 66572. 1, Wing. Arrow points to a defect in the wing where the distal portion of the wing has shifted anteriorly relative to the basal portion causing an upwards curving of the basal portion of Rs; 2, Line drawing of the wing. Scale bar equals 3.0 mm (1)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3990309/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

